wikipedia_page.main: George Payne (22 August 1921 – 6 April 1987) was an English footballer who played as a goalkeeper for Tranmere Rovers and Northwich Victoria. He made 467 appearances for Tranmere.

response: * George Payne, English footballer, died in Thingwall.
